# Prompt History Logging

Append entries to the appropriate `ai-prompts/*.md` file after major tasks.

| Activity | File |
|----------|------|
| Planning | `ai-prompts/planning.md` |
| Design | `ai-prompts/design.md` |
| Implementation | `ai-prompts/implementation.md` |
| Testing | `ai-prompts/testing.md` |
| Debugging | `ai-prompts/debugging.md` |
| Code review | `ai-prompts/code-review.md` |
| Documentation | `ai-prompts/documentation.md` |

## Entry template

```markdown
---

## YYYY-MM-DD — Phase

**Objective:** ...

**Prompt:** ...

**AI Response Summary:** ...

**Accepted:** ...

**Modified:** ...

**Rejected:** ...

**Reason:** ...
```

Use `TODO` for review fields when not yet recorded. Never overwrite — append only.
